Summary:
Microsoft and Sony are both vying get your hard-earned money this holiday season. But which game console should you buy: the Xbox One of the PS4?
‘Tis the season for some big decisions: Fake tree or real tree? Self-gifting or hoping for the best? And, of course: which new game console should you get — Microsoft’s Xbox One, or Sony’s PlayStation 4?
Both consoles offer some unique features for gamers, both come with different launch titles, and both have different cord-cutting takes on watching TV and online video. In this guide, we are breaking it all down. But don’t just take our word for it — also go and read some other reviews out there. We’ve linked to some of the best, and rounded it all up with our own buying recommendations.
